[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0612","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0372","title":"Microsoft BackOffice Server 安装程序敏感信息泄露漏洞","description":"BackOffice Server 安装程序在安装过程中会将账户名和密码以明文形式写入 reboot.ini 配置文件中，安装完成后未自动删除该文件，导致敏感信息泄露。本地攻击者可通过读取该文件获取系统账户凭据，进而提升权限或进行横向移动。该漏洞影响 Microsoft BackOffice Server 相关版本，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低，攻击者需具备本地文件读取权限。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0372"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-12T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.307","remediation":"安装 BackOffice Server 4.0 完成后，立即手动删除 `<系统盘>:\\Program Files\\Microsoft Backoffice\\Reboot.ini` 文件，该文件包含 SQL Executive、Exchange Services 和 MTS Remote Administration 账户的明文密码。无论安装成功或失败，均须执行删除操作。删除后该文件不会自动重建，除非重新安装 BackOffice 4.0。同时建议限制本地登录权限，仅允许管理员访问服务器。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ217004","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-005","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19192","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/8600ac0c091970175de0b53d9682f50858aef8dc/1999/CVE-1999-0372.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0372","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0372.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-gcm6-ww8r-qm6x/GHSA-gcm6-ww8r-qm6x.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0372.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0612.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0611","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0371","title":"Lynx lynx 本地符号链接敏感文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Lynx 文本浏览器在处理临时文件时存在不安全的符号链接跟踪漏洞。本地攻击者可通过在 /tmp 目录下预创建指向目标敏感文件的符号链接，诱导 Lynx 将临时数据写入该链接指向的文件，从而覆盖系统关键文件，导致数据破坏或权限提升。利用条件为攻击者拥有本地账户权限且 Lynx 以当前用户权限运行。该漏洞影响早期版本 Lynx，CVSS 评分 1.2，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":1.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0371"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-11T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.167","remediation":"升级 Lynx 至 2.7.1 或更高版本，该版本已改用 mkstemp() 安全创建临时文件，避免预测 /tmp 路径导致的竞争条件。如无法升级，确保 /tmp 目录设置粘滞位（chmod 1777 /tmp），并通过设置环境变量 TMPDIR 指向用户私有临时目录来缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0371"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0611.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0610","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0370","title":"Sun Solaris 与 SunOS man 及 catman 任意文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 和 SunOS 系统中的 man 与 catman 命令存在文件覆盖漏洞，本地攻击者可通过利用这些命令在处理临时文件时的缺陷，将任意文件写入目标系统上的指定路径，实现文件覆盖或权限提升。该漏洞影响 Sun Solaris 及 SunOS 多个版本，CVSS 评分 4.6，攻击者需拥有本地系统访问权限。厂商已发布相应安全补丁修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0370"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:15.047","remediation":"建议升级到 Sun 官方补丁对应的 Solaris 版本（如 Solaris 2.6 及更新版本已修复此问题），或从 sunsolve.sun.com 获取 man/catman 相关安全补丁。临时缓解措施：以 root 权限执行 `chmod 755 /usr/bin/man /usr/bin/catman` 移除 setuid 位，防止普通用户利用提权覆盖任意文件。同时通过 `tty` 访问控制限制本地用户登录高危账户。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/165"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0610.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0585","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0353","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9107,\"outputTokens\":28,\"totalTokens\":10799}}","description":"HP-UX 系统中的 rpc.pcnfsd 服务存在权限配置错误漏洞，远程未经身份认证的攻击者可通过修改主打印机假脱机目录的权限，获取远程 root 权限访问。该漏洞影响 HP-UX 多个版本，CVSS 评分 9.3，危害等级严重。攻击者无需认证即可远程利用，通过篡改打印机假脱机目录权限实现权限提升至 root 权限，严重威胁系统安全。建议升级至修复版本或禁用 rpc.pcnfsd 服务。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":9.3,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0353"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-10T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.860","remediation":"升级 HP-UX 到最新的Patched-Up 11.11 或更高版本，并应用最新的安全补丁包。具体步骤：1. 执行\"swinstall -s /somepath/hpus11v1_patch\"安装补丁；2. 检查并删除不必要的rpc.pcnfsd服务，使其处于禁用状态；3. 在防火墙上配置规则，仅允许本地网络段访问rpc.pcnfsd端口；4. 验证/spool目录的权限，确保持有者为root且权限为755，禁止其他用户修改。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-026.shtml","http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9902-091","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0353","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0353.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj/GHSA-2cv7-m7r7-5xxj.json","https://github.com/blackhook/nessus-plugins/blob/64177d96abbb07c58cf7e131046b067ebc61fcb5/h/hpux_PHCO_14625.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0353.json","https://github.com/Freem93/grammar_nasl_v2/blob/63834ebb8cd6e97050e155291c7500ad53bb20c6/plugins/hpux_PHKL_15689.nasl","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x6000/5377/info.html","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0585.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0648","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0407","title":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 `/IISADMPWD` 默认虚拟目录暴力破解与用户枚举漏洞","description":"Microsoft IIS 4.0 默认安装中包含 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录，该目录下的文件可用作暴力破解密码攻击的代理，攻击者可通过发送大量认证请求尝试枚举系统有效用户或破解弱口令，无需特殊权限。此漏洞影响 IIS 4.0 版本，攻击者只需网络可达即可利用，可能导致账户信息泄露和未授权访问。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0407"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.880","remediation":"建议立即删除 IIS 4.0 中默认创建的 /IISADMPWD 虚拟目录（映射路径 c:\\winnt\\system32\\inetsrv\\iisadmpwd），通过 IIS 管理控制台移除该虚拟目录映射即可消除风险。如确需使用 Web 密码修改功能，必须配置 SSL 证书，并将 Metabase 中的 PasswordChangeFlags 属性值从默认的 1 改为 0（强制仅允许 SSL 通道修改密码），同时在域级别启用账户锁定策略（连续 5 次失败后锁定 30 分钟）以缓解暴力破解。建议升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统以获取受支持的 IIS 版本。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91983486431506&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=92000623021036&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0648.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0604","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0368","title":"WU-FTPD 和 ProFTPD realpath 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"wu-ftpd 及 ProFTPD 的 realpath 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向目标 FTP 服务器发送特制的路径请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出并实现远程 root 权限获取。该漏洞影响 wu-ftpd 2.4.2、ProFTPD 1.2 pre1 及 SCO Open Server 5.0.5 等版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布安全更新修复此漏洞。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0368"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.780","remediation":"升级 wu-ftpd 至 2.5.0 及以上版本，或升级 ProFTPD 至 1.2.0 及以上稳定版。如无法立即升级，可在 inetd/xinetd 配置中禁用 FTP 服务或限制可信任 IP 访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0368","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19087","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/REMath/implementations/blob/045b59dc77d5bd3e9a14713898ebcfdebacd11e9/tanalysis/tanalysis/verisec%20v1.0/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0368","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0368.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g/GHSA-pjq9-4mrj-pv4g.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/westtide/open-source-case-studies/blob/57e71842cdb3e034316b0d083f8d19f680501b67/verisec/.frama-c/programs_apps_wu-ftpd_CVE-1999-0368_realpath-linkpath_prefix_ok.eva/nonterm.log","https://github.com/tomhart-msc/verisec/blob/02f3a9660885181705e7550b8609534bbbaa414c/programs/apps/wu-ftpd/CVE-1999-0368/README","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0368.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0604.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0603","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0367","title":"NetBSD netstat 本地内核内存访问漏洞","description":"NetBSD 系统的 netstat 命令存在本地内核内存泄露漏洞。由于 netstat 工具在处理网络统计信息时未能正确限制对内核内存区域的访问权限，本地攻击者可通过执行特制的 netstat 命令读取内核敏感数据，导致内核信息泄露。该漏洞影响早期 NetBSD 版本，攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限才能利用，CVSS 评分 2.1，危害等级低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0367"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.657","remediation":"升级 NetBSD 至 1.4.1 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 NetBSD 1.4.1 的安全补丁中修复。如无法升级，可通过 chmod 700 /usr/bin/netstat 限制 netstat 命令的执行权限，仅允许 root 用户使用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/7571"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0603.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0578","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0350","title":"Rational Software ClearCase db_loader 竞态条件本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Rational Software ClearCase for Unix 3.2 中的 db_loader 程序存在竞争条件漏洞。本地用户可利用该程序在处理 SUID 位时的竞态缺陷，通过精心构造的时序攻击绕过权限检查，将普通文件权限提升至 root 级别。攻击者需具有本地系统访问权限并精确控制竞争窗口，成功利用后可获取目标系统的完全控制权，CVSS 评分 6.2，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":6.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0350"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-08T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:12.480","remediation":"升级 Rational ClearCase 至 3.2.1 及以上版本，官方已修复 db_loader 中的竞态条件问题。如无法升级，可手动移除 db_loader 程序的 SUID 位（chmod u-s /path/to/db_loader），并限制仅授权用户可执行该程序，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0350","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19429"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0578.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0601","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0366","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 网络共享空密码认证绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 存在空密码认证绕过漏洞。由于系统在处理空 NT 哈希值时存在缺陷，远程攻击者可通过使用空密码直接访问目标系统的网络共享资源，无需提供有效凭据。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，攻击者利用此漏洞可获取共享文件及敏感数据的读取权限，危害程度较高。Microsoft 已在安全公告 MS99-004 中发布修复更新。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0366"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-08","updated":"1999-02-08","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-004 提供的修补程序（对应 KB 文章 Q214840），该补丁修正了 Windows NT 4.0 Service Pack 4 中 SAM 认证逻辑错误。如无法安装补丁，可禁用域控制器上来自 DOS/Windows 3.1/Windows for Workgroups/OS/2/Macintosh 客户端的密码更改功能作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/d92a0abc5d3abac6dcdfabfef6fd71c158e0fd8b/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0366","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0366.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/58eef6eedd760f280b47bfb4c94db9995b29c5a0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/6eca843f42fd99fea8c9b630931afac7c9d4576c/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5/GHSA-5fcq-r7m3-pxf5.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0366.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--e0b64613-6d45-4a3b-8434-c9c2ceedf571.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000517.txt","https://github.com/zephyros1603/RadiantProcessors/blob/7d44cb1cd4b9e088fbe463f1b19be50a04c2efe8/Backend/RAG/data/allitems.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0601.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0599","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0599.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0365","title":"Metamail mailcap 条目未过滤 shell 元字符远程命令执行漏洞","description":"metamail 邮件处理工具包中存在 shell 元字符注入漏洞，在将邮件内容传递给 mailcap 条目处理时未对 shell 元字符进行正确引号转义，导致远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制邮件触发命令执行。攻击者利用该漏洞可在受害者系统上以当前用户权限执行任意命令，影响广泛部署 metamail 的 Unix/Linux 系统。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0365"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-04T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:14.403","remediation":"升级 metamail 至 2.7-9 或更高版本，该版本已对 mailcap 文件中的 shell 元字符进行正确转义处理。如无法升级，可临时移除或禁用系统中所有不可信来源的 mailcap 配置项，同时限制邮件客户端自动调用 metamail 处理附件。在 sendmail 环境下，建议禁用自动执行 mailcap 条目的功能，并审查 /etc/mailcap 及用户 ~/.mailcap 中的每条规则，确保不含未引用的 shell 元字符。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0365.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0365","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0365.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f