害等级中危，受影响用户应升级至更高版本以修复此问题。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0362"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-02-02T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:13.990","remediation":"升级至 WS_FTP Server 1.0.3 及以上版本可修复此漏洞；在防火墙中限制 FTP 服务端口的访问来源 IP，防止未授权远程连接发起 CWD 命令攻击。鉴于该产品版本过于老旧，建议迁移至受支持的最新版 WS_FTP Server 或替代 FTP 服务软件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.eeye.com/html/Research/Advisories/AD02021999.html","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/217","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0cda26301f5b3e56ace35e3d98835812d878db41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0362","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0362.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/638fc08494602a9faf37bf81043122f16d26625c/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/nessus/nessus-plugins/scripts/wsftp_cwd_dos.nasl","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0362.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/scipag/AttackToolKit/blob/78bf88564956b8f18a37659dc3d345093e95a136/plugins/Ipswitch%20WS_FTP%20Server%20prior%205.0.2%20CWD%20path%20denial%20of%20service.plugin","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0594.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0714","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0459","title":"Linux Alpha MILO 本地拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Alpha Linux 系统中存在本地拒绝服务漏洞。本地攻击者可通过 MILO 引导加载程序强制系统重新启动，导致系统服务不可用。该漏洞影响运行 Alpha Linux 的 DEC Alpha 架构系统，攻击者需具备本地访问权限，无需高权限即可利用，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0459"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:26.440","remediation":"建议升级 MILO 引导程序至最新版本，并限制系统本地用户的登录访问权限。在生产环境中应禁用不必要的本地用户账号，并通过 `/etc/security/access.conf` 或 PAM 模块限制控制台访问。对于 Alpha 架构系统，可考虑迁移至更新的 Linux 内核版本以规避该引导层问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0459"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0714.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0644","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0403","title":"Cyrix CPU on Linux 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Linux 系统中 Cyrix CPU 存在硬件设计缺陷，本地攻击者可通过执行特定指令序列触发处理器异常，导致系统崩溃或拒绝服务。该漏洞影响使用 Cyrix 处理器的 Linux 系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户权限才能利用，无法远程触发。CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0403"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-02-01T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:19.373","remediation":"建议升级 Linux 内核至 2.2.x 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续内核更新中修复。如无法升级，可通过禁用 Cyrix CPU 特定优化功能或限制本地用户访问权限作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=91821080015725&w=2"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0644.toml"}]